\mu^*(B)=\inf\bigg\{\sum_{A\in\mathcal{C}}\mu_o(A):\mathcal{C}\textrm{ is a countable subset of }\mathcal{A}\textrm{ such that }B\subseteq\bigcup_{A\in\mathcal{C}}A\bigg\}.
